{"tid":1832782,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2020日本小姐出爐　大三「學霸正妹」奪冠私照曝光美翻","createTime":"2020-01-21T11:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:51:32.000Z","uid":32511,"like":194,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"4a47838ecf560ece904742f6c7ef5cf01e67c7cb","tid":1832782,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/21/2371170-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2F2371170-XXL.jpg&h=f28f2b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/21/2371209-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2F2371209-XXL.jpg&h=6e343247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/21/2371169-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2F2371169-XXL.jpg&h=b2b0c841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/21/2371208-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2F2371208-XXL.jpg&h=f5917e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/21/2371207-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2F2371207-XXL.jpg&h=8705e159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從1950年開始舉辦的日本小姐大賽，每一次參加的人數都相當多，不過考核標準也超嚴格，除了宗旨為「展現日本美」之外，還會對參賽者的品行、外貌與私下態度進行檢視，以往女星包含藤原紀香等人都是從日本小姐出道，而近日2020年的日本小姐冠軍也跟著出爐，是一名21歲，來自日本名校慶應義塾大學的小田安珠奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n這次一共有2525人報名參加，最終闖進決賽的僅有15位，年齡大多都在25歲以下，最小的更還有18歲剛成年的女性，而小田安珠順利從2千多人中脫穎而出，成為第52代日本小姐，今年大三的她，受到電影影響熱愛考古學，也因此主修考古相關學系，是個內外兼具的女性，而她也透露自己的夢想是成為主播，從社群平台上不難看出平常的活動相當多。<br />\n <br />\n奪下冠軍寶座後，小田安珠也開心的在IG上曬出自己奪冠的照片，並感性寫下「當叫到我的名字時，我真的非常感動，從區域資格賽開始就一直受到大家的祝福，也非常感謝跟我一起入圍的所有決賽者！從明天開始我會好好發揮自己的能力，希望對社會有所貢獻！」底下網友也紛紛湧入送出恭喜留言，希望她的未來一切順利。"},{"pid":"7f641048263410592c44cc4ea862e6d750e7bc0c","tid":1832782,"uid":2889,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b06a4528a1517bd2829106c5777363efdfe64cf","tid":1832782,"uid":7343,"like":65,"dislike":31,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"個樣假假地"},{"pid":"f200069bbeb70868e080dd16ca0054882b74ba21","tid":1832782,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db10b8a35146098940d041dd7511ab17704f5f7","tid":1832782,"uid":133533,"like":167,"dislike":3,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"笑得好假"},{"pid":"d6961bf13ded93692bb311379bf6d3565e69e204","tid":1832782,"uid":289751,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"7b06a4528a1517bd2829106c5777363efdfe64cf","tid":1832782,"uid":7343,"like":65,"dislike":31,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"個樣假假地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:46:30.000Z","msg":"對眼唔知, 不過個鼻應該有整"},{"pid":"2cd3bd3a3be10759a51d6130aa973a888a585387","tid":1832782,"uid":20115,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:46:50.000Z","msg":"良烈唯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a21d2a0d9d146465bbfedb8bbdb6d9efb6c42f","tid":1832782,"uid":55386,"like